name: Day 4 of Quarantine: Disappointment
description: From all the feelings up to now, all the thoughts could not escape. The only thing I could blame was myself for what it is now. That's the truth. But, it does not stop someone from feeling drown and desperate right? What if I did this, what if I put in more effort, what if, what if and another what if... I cannot change the past, no one can. Does not matter whether how much I beg or wish, nothing is going to change now. Just cry again, I suppose.
